            . I am a watchman. I was called, and saw the prosecutor holding the prisoner by the collar; he gave him in charge for robbing him. I found 2 s. 11 1/2 d. on him. I saw no money on the ground; the prosecutor pulled out 3 s., and said that was all he had left.</p>
